ore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有, zurich, chubb"},{"pid":"029a499fd419241ed4ab7fe1190be2792fcbe203","tid":196273,"uid":84949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:25:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果班機臨時取消左，要買另一間航空公司嘅機票<br />\n邊間賠得最好最多？有無可能全數賠足 ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：買左香草航空，驚驚地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nif the flight is cancel/ delay because of operational reasons...then i think no insurance companies will cover"},{"pid":"2b543de5061426c9b036285981cef2d0ff99b9ad","tid":196273,"uid":9323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:29:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果班機臨時取消左，要買另一間航空公司嘅機票<br />\n邊間賠得最好最多？有無可能全數賠足 ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：買左香草航空，驚驚地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nif the flight is cancel/ delay because of operational reasons...then i think no insurance companies will cover</blockquote><br />\n我上次就係咁 不過係uo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買左zurich上限5000 你買另外一班機要係你原本班機嘅6個鐘後  <br />\n我咁岩買左張ana機票 6個鐘後飛$4900 <br />\n已claim 足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17b8002c1d1edbda4cb43de6fbd4ad968b00e03d","tid":196273,"uid":84949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:29:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果班機臨時取消左，要買另一間航空公司嘅機票<br />\n邊間賠得最好最多？有無可能全數賠足 ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：買左香草航空，驚驚地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係第一次坐廉航，買左UO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗我最緊要保電話、基本財物證件、delay/臨時cancel呢類野<br />\n醫療反而唔太擔心 都係去東京食玩訓 應該無咩危險</blockquote><br />\n醫療先緊要,由其日